924,"6. COFFEE FLIP
","6. COFFEE FLIP
",COFFEE FLIP,"Wow. This makes the cobwebs run screaming.
 1 ounce cognac
 1 ounce tawny port
 1 small egg
 1 teaspoon sugar
  Fill cocktail shaker with ice.
