93,"11. MAY BLOSSOM FIZZ
","11. MAY BLOSSOM FIZZ
",MAY BLOSSOM FIZZ,"As sweetly intoxicating as springtime flowers. Your guests just may frolic around the May Pole.
 1 teaspoon grenadine
 1/2 ounce lemon juice
 1 ounce club soda
 2 ounces Punsch
  Fill cocktail shaker with ice.
  Add grenadine, lemon juice, club soda, and Punsch.
  Shake.
  Strain into an old-fashioned glass.
