919,"298. FDR'S MARTINI
","298. FDR'S MARTINI
",FDR'S MARTINI,"Fireside Chats are much more pleasant with a pitcher of these nearby. Make this drink your New Deal.
 1 ounce gin
 1/2 ounce vermouth
 1 teaspoon olive brine
  Fill cocktail shaker with ice.
  Add gin, vermouth, and olive brine.
  Stir.
  Rub a lemon twist around the rim of a chilled martini glass.
  Strain into the glass.
  Garnish with an olive.
