","794. SHERRY COBBLER
",SHERRY COBBLER,"Santa Claus likes for a sherry to greet him in England on Christmas Eve. Not milk.
 2 ounces club soda
 1 teaspoon sugar
 2 1/2 ounces sherry
 1/2 ounce orange juice
  Fill a double old-fashioned glass with crushed ice.
  Add club soda, sugar, sherry, and orange juice.
  Garnish with fruit.
