634,"813. EGGNOG CARIBBEAN STYLE
","813. EGGNOG CARIBBEAN STYLE
",EGGNOG CARIBBEAN STYLE,"Bring out the nog and the Christmas calypso music and watch Aunt Margo shimmy the night away.
