","996. NATIONAL ANTHEM
",NATIONAL ANTHEM,"British in its origin, the National Anthem cure ""soon gets you on your feet,"" so sayeth the Avengers' John Steed, con-summate Brit, consummate drinker, sure to know how to shake off last night's indulgence and quickly return to sav-ing the world.
 1 egg
 3 or 4 dashes Worcestershire sauce Dash salt
  Mix well.
  Down quickly.
