149,"997. PRAIRIE OYSTER
","997. PRAIRIE OYSTER
",PRAIRIE OYSTER,"It's the catsup in this one that makes those pesky morning-after demons vanish.
 1 teaspoon Worcestershire sauce
 2 dashes vinegar
 Dash pepper
 1 teaspoon tomato catsup
 1 egg yolk
  Fill cocktail shaker with ice.
  Add Worcestershire sauce, vinegar, pepper, and tomato catsup.
  Shake.
  Strain into an old-fashioned glass.
  Drop in egg yolk without breaking yolk.
